      "side": 1,
      "message": "Break it into two different interfaces, so that existing brokers will still work, without the need of adding incomplete/broken default implementations of the new methods.\n\n```suggestion\n  Set\u003cTopicSubscriberWithGroupId\u003e topicSubscribersWithGroupId();\n}\n\npublic interface ExtendedBrokerApi extends BrokerApi {\n  /**\n```",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 86,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 88,
        "endChar": 5
      },
      "revId": "273162b6d5404474d678876c6b76ec7957d7a880",
